  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give Hope to 120 Widows and Orphans in Cameroon</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Since January 2017, growing violence between government and separatists&apos; armed groups has forced families of the South-West and North-West Regions to leave their villages and towns. Many have lost everything to indiscriminate fire. This project will help 120 of them start again by providing cash transfers to families. BIRDS is the only humanitarian actor providing cash transfers in the whole Lebialem Division right now.</narrative>
  </description>
